<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>12792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝拉：哦，不！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>丹尼：怎么了？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝拉：哈皮安去哪儿了？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>丹尼：他是个大人。他能照顾好自己。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>丹尼：你闻到什么了吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝拉：闻起来很香！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布朗：我闻起来那像是早餐！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三个人：早上好，哈皮安。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：早上好。我做了些早餐。请坐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>丹尼：呃，也许我们可以在地板上吃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：我有个主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：你们吃早餐吧。你们需要力气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：同时，我给你们讲特雷西的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：这些信息可能对你们有帮助。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：他一直在偷我们世界的颜色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：特雷西成长的时候，他很正常，就像其他巨人一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：我年轻的时候，我有很多朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：特雷西没有我幸运。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：他从来没跟和我，或我的朋友们玩儿过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93159</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：我们会邀请他加入我们，但他永远不会。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：也许是因为他的毛不如我们的亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：后来有一天，他做了件坏事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：他朝我扔了块石头，把我弄伤了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111430</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：我生气地去追他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：我比特雷西大，但他跑得更快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：我追他追到了山那边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布朗：你抓到他了吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：没有。当他跑上山的时候，岩石松了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：在他身后滚下来堵住了那条路，所以没人能跟上去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：他一路爬到了山顶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：今天，上山的路还是堵着的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>丹尼：那你就再也没有报复过他了？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：我不想伤害他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：我只想告诉他他伤害了我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：可是，特雷西在山顶上发生了什么事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝拉：什么事？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：当他到达山顶时，特雷西坐下来哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162623</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：他充满了嫉妒和仇恨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：他的眼泪是黑色的，到处都是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：他当时不知道，但山顶充满了魔力。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：他用拳头猛击地面。火花四溅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：他没有注意到火花，但他感觉不一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：他伸手去拿附近的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：那是一朵红花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：突然间，它变成了灰色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布朗：从那时候，他开始偷颜色的吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：我不知道。很多年没人见到他了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：我和我的朋友们长大后都忘记了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：现在他回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈皮安：他用他的力量偷走了我们的颜色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>丹尼：我们必须阻止他！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
